text: Incredible opportunity to buy a park model home at The Glen at Maple Falls! Health issues force sale. This '94 Wedgewood Park park model is in good shape. When you step in the back door, you have a private sunken primary bedroom. Above the bedroom is a loft for 2 to 4 people. Then, there is another door that has 2 private bunks! Full size bath, and plenty of room in the kitchen, with a dining area. Large living room area. This also has a covered deck for barbequing. Firepit out front ready for entertaining! Also has storage shed. Everything there stays! The Glen has 2 pools (1 open year-round) hot tub, sauna, tennis & pickleball courts, river access, 24/7 security, laundry & shower facilities, trails, and so much more. Minutes to Mt. Baker!

This charming Lakeridge condo overlooks Sudden Valley's natural beauty in desirable Gate 2. Spacious & sun-filled home offers vaulted living room ceilings & privacy throughout. It has 2 sizeable bedrooms + office/bonus room that counts as a 3rd room & ample storage. Featuring both front & back decks, a sunny back deck where you can enjoy mountain & golf course views plus glimpses of Lake Whatcom & a private front porch that can be enjoyed as a shady oasis for peace & quiet. Friendly Lakeridge community fees cover a private pool, pickleball/tennis court & water/sewer. Access to scenic Lake Louise Trail just out your door & many beaches, trails & parks to explore throughout Sudden Valley. Great home or investment property, not at rental cap!

This delightful home, with its timeless charm and solid structure, offers an incredible opportunity for investment and customization. The standout feature of this property is its sprawling private yard, perfect for outdoor entertaining, gardening, or simply enjoying your own slice of serenity. Imagine summer barbecues, gatherings, or peaceful evenings in this beautiful, expansive space. Located in the vibrant, welcoming community of Ferndale, you have all the local amenities, parks, trails and shops near by, as well as 4 min I-5 access! With its friendly neighborhood and excellent schools, its potential for updates and the exceptional value of its large yard, this home is a true gem. Act quicklyproperties like this are hard to find!

One of Bellingham's earlier homes in a well established and highly sought after neighborhood. Located in the Cornwall Park neighborhood it is an easy walk to both Cornwall and Broadway Parks. Off street parking in front and alley access with garage in the back. Nice little deck and fenced yard area. One level 1640 sf home with hardwood floors, 2 bedrooms and a fantastic 560 sf basement area. One walk thru and the possibilities jump out, so much to appreciate here. This 1924 beauty deserves a little TLC. Perfectly fine as is but is ready for some deferred maintenance and is priced accordingly.
neighborhoods: Cornwall Park, Broadway Park Historic District
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Bellingham Public Schools

text: Welcome Home to your Bright, Top Floor Lynden Condo. Set in a Peaceful and Social 55+ Community, this Spacious 2013 built Home offers tall ceilings, a cozy Fireplace, and tons of Natural light, Primary bath with walk-in shower. Upgrades include Primary bedroom ceiling fan, smart control thermostat for HVAC; Kitchen under cabinet LED lighting and upgraded soft close drawers. Your unit enjoys its own, large/deep garage with included storage racks and floor matting. The Building shares several common areas for neighbor or gatherings, both indoor and outjoin in the Friday Happy Hour! Outside your doors, find Bender Fields and several walking routes, Homestead Fitness and Steakhouse 9 Restaurant/Bar.

Live full-time or vacation just minutes from the beach in the picturesque beachfront community of Birch Bay, Washington. This affordable home boasts an excellent floor plan with a kitchen, open living room, and one bathroom, alongside two bedrooms for comfort and convenience. Enjoy ample parking with two assigned spaces and plenty of guest parking available. Immerse yourself in the vibrant coastal lifestyle of Birch Bay, offering beach walks, clamming, crabbing, waterslides, restaurants, and shops. Plus, indoor cats and friendly dogs welcome, every member of your clan can enjoy the coastal paradise of Birch Bay.

Meticulously maintained 3 yr new single level rambler on large professionally landscaped lot 15 min from DT B'ham. Escape to your private oasis nestled up to a protected wooded greenbelt. Custom steel raised planter boxes and outdoor firepit w/berries, fruit trees, sauna, gas plumbed grill, covered patio space and sprinkler system allow you to sit back, relax, and enjoy your surroundings. Approach your rocking chair front porch and enter into open oversized spaces, SS appliances, pendant lighting, custom tiled primary bath w/Todo toilet, 3 large bedrooms and dedicated office space. Better than new w/each detail thought out making this property truly move in ready.

Discover this beautifully updated 4-bedroom, 2.25-bath Ferndale gem! Set on a spacious 9, 000+ sq. ft. lot in a scenic neighborhood, this 1, 872 sq. ft. two-level home blends modern finishes with cozy charm. Enjoy a kitchen with new appliances and quartz countertops, relax in the inviting living spaces, and appreciate the energy efficiency of electric furnace and heat pump for heating and cooling and a gas tankless water heater. Outdoors, a large backyard offers ample space for gardening, gatherings, and play, while a welcoming front porch and back deck invite year-round enjoyment. Complete with an attached garage, driveway, and extra parking, this home is perfect for Northwest living!

Embrace the potential of this estate property nestled by the tranquil Nooksack River. Spanning 2.25 acres of park-like grounds adorned with a serene pond and majestic cedar and fir trees, this home features a metal roof, inviting skylights, and the promise of a stunning fireplace as its centerpiece. Imagine the allure of leisurely evenings on the porch, accompanied by the soothing sounds of the river and local wildlife. Originally envisioned as a charming bed and breakfast, this property invites you to revive that dream or transform it into your ideal retreat. Conveniently located close to the Mount Baker Recreation area, where on can indulge in hiking, winter sports, fishing, and simply basking in nature's embrace.

Come visit this home located in Baker Ridge, a gated community. It is front row facing east w/unobstructed views of Mt. Baker & the Twin Sisters. The home features a gourmet kitchen w/ample cabinets & counter space. Main floor features elegant primary suite, living & dining & family room. There are built in cabinets throughout & lots of storage. The main floor also features bedroom plus bath, powder room & spacious laundry room. Attached 3 car garage w/no threshold.Upper level has 2 bedrooms w/access to their own baths, great room w/kitchen & unfinished bonus room w/access to the garage. Multiple patios to enjoy the outside. Includes a 1418 sq. ft. 2X6 stick framed shop with loft. Community features a pickleball/basketball court plus more.

Charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath home with 1, 839 sq. ft. of living space on a quiet street, close to schools and a neighborhood park. This home features a cozy living room with a gas fireplace, air conditioning for year-round comfort, and a large front porch. The backyard includes a patio and a convenient shed for extra storage. An attached 2-car garage with alley access completes the package.

Rare offering on the south side - stunning luxury contemporary home situated on a 60 waterfront lot with no bank. Showcasing panoramic vistas of Mt. Baker, the San Juan Islands, and the Marina Breakwater. All year-round living, open, and light-filled living spaces that extend to the outdoors with expansive decks on both exposures. Architect-designed home featuring 3 beds, a main level den/office, and 3 baths. Private courtyard, a double car garage, and marina access right around the corner. Experience waterfront living in beautiful Point Roberts, less than 30 minutes from Vancouver, BC.

Welcome to Harborside Estates, where this charming home combines fantastic curb appeal with a prime location just minutes from Blaines vibrant downtown and local schools. Step inside to find a beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath retreat with an office. Featuring 9' ceilings, a modern kitchen with sleek grey cabinets, quartz countertops, air conditioning, and stainless steel appliances...this home is turnkey and move in ready. The primary suite offers a relaxing space with vaulted ceilings, a private balcony, and serene Birch Bay water views. Outside, enjoy a fully fenced backyard just steps from Montfort Park and easy beach access. Plus, a spacious 3-car garage awaits your vehicles and storage needs.

This updated rambler with a shop in a quiet mid-county neighborhood is the perfect place to call home! Fresh updates from floor to ceiling make this home turn-key! You'll love the new LVP flooring and white trim, updated bathroom, newer paint inside and out, and modern light fixtures. Cozy up in the living room with the freestanding propane fireplace that heats the whole home. Outside, you'll enjoy updated landscaping, fully fenced backyard, garden area, fire pit, great patio space for entertaining, a shed, and a two-car heated garage/shop. Plenty of parking for rv's/boats, etc. The location can't be beat- just a short drive to the freeway, centrally located to many amenities, and part of the Lynden School Dist.

Better than new stunning sun-drenched modern farmhouse on 5+ acres. Radiating PNW charm, the curb appeal sets the stage + every thoughtfully executed detail is spot on. Lives like a single level home (with only a bonus space above the 3 car garage), you'll love the ceiling height, open concept floor plan and the custom high end finishes. The primary suite is privately located away from the other 2 bedrooms and boasts a luxurious ensuite with under mount soaker tub & tiled shower. Energy efficient mini splits for heating/cooling, solar panels, LVP flooring, hand blown glass lights made from molds from the 1800s, covered back patio & delightful English garden vibe in the backyard. Bonus: RV pad with 50 amp power, water & sewer dump.

This Gorgeous 4 bedroom 3 bathroom contemporary home is just what you have been looking for. Located in a very desirable Sudden Valley Community. Minutes to Whatcom Lake, Private Beaches, Trails, Playgrounds, Clubhouse, Community Pool, Tennis Court ect. All of this at a very affordable Price. Not too large, But extremely cozy. Just the Place to call Home.

Nestled on a sprawling half acre lot, you won't find another one like this fully remodeled mid-century Craftsmen. Blending timeless character and modern convenience, it boasts a full updated kitchen with brass light fixtures, paneled appliances and cabinets by local craftsmen Wurtz Furniture and high end Wolf and Z Line appliances. Solidly constructed with fir floors throughout and reclaimed timber beams, the home has been fully remodeled including insulation, solid fir doors with Emtec handles and ductless HVAC system. The parcel consists of 3 legal lots for massive development potential as the city grows. Finish it off with a serviced RV space, garage with plumbing and electrical stubs ready for a new bathroom and you're all set!

One of a kind single level penthouse with bay, island, city, and epic sunset views in a coveted location at iconic Taylor Dock in Fairhaven! This stunning NEW residence represents a highly sought after boutique building, rarely available! Timeless sophistication with captivating design elements & top of the line finishes throughout. Enjoy walls of glass, soaring ceilings, and folding glass doors opening to a large, covered sundeck. Other features include 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, office, chef's kitchen, air conditioning, and a private 2 car garage. The feel of a single family home with the lock and leave lifestyle of a condo. Enjoy daily walks on the dock and Fairhaven's vibrant village with restaurants, stores, parks, all only steps away!

Discover the charm of this well-kept 4-bedroom home on a corner lot in the desirable Park at Homestead community. Step onto the inviting covered front porch, ideal for unwinding after a long day. Inside, the spacious open-concept living area features a cozy fireplace in the living room, a dining area, and a bright kitchen with a convenient island eating space. Host gatherings on the patio just off the dining area, perfect for BBQs. Large primary suite with a 3/4 ensuite bath plus three additional bedrooms and a full bath upstairs. Enjoy new flooring, A/C, and the convenience of a two-car garage with driveway parking. Plus, a play area in front of the home adds to the appeal. This home is a must see! 1 Year Home Warranty Included!

Wonderfully maintained and much-loved brick rambler located in the desirable Montfort Park neighborhood, offering serene views of Drayton Harbor. Situated on a peaceful dead-end street in a storybook setting w/ a private backyard oasis. Just a stone's throw from Hughes Bayview & Montfort Park, where you'll enjoy access to scenic hiking trails and lookout points. Minutes from Semiahmoo Resort & Spa near all of the amenities Blaine has to offer. Original custom design with wide, open spaces, the home is both comfortable & accessible. Recent updates include gas furnace and electric hot water tank, ensuring efficiency and peace of mind. With potential for expansion upward don't miss the opportunity to make this clean, well-kept home your own!

Heres your chance to own a builders custom home on a large corner lot in one of the most coveted neighborhoods in Lynden. Main-level living including a spacious primary suite connected to a private courtyard with a covered porch. Upstairs youll find 3 bedrooms, a home office, and a large bonus room with surround sound. Youll love the custom details including open-beam ceilings, Juliet balcony, built-ins, stonework, and hand-scraped hardwood floors. Other amenities include a large 2-car garage and central A/C. This home seamlessly blends craftsmanship and modern comfort. Don't miss out!

This lovingly maintained Mallard trailer sits on a corner lot in division two. Trees give some privacy from the road, and a shed sits on the property for additional or larger storage. With two sleeping places, and a cozy living room, there is lots of space to relax and enjoy the comforts of this home away from home. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Beautiful new construction quality built by Pacific Edge Builders custom home on quiet dead end street. Desirable Whispering Meadows neighborhood is Nooksack's newest development surrounded by protected open space and waterways. This one level 3 bed, 2 bath home features open concept living space which truly feels large. Primary bedroom with walk in closet, tiled flooring and backsplash w/ quartz countertops. Kitchen with stainless appliances, quarts countertops, full height backsplash tile & custom cabinets and large pantry. Large covered patio abutting open space and mature trees provide a private backyard great for entertaining year round. Located close to schools, parks, restaurants, & the Canadian border. Vacant & move in ready!

Immaculate cared for this 2nd owner home in a great neighborhood & adjacent to an 8 acre city owned park. This home is move in ready with recent updates to flooring and baths. 4 could be 5 bedrooms, 3 baths, 2 large living areas, lower level could be another suite with few changes. Large kitchen with lots of cabinets and spacious center island. Spacious rooms throughout, lots of storage plus oversized garage with shop area, newer furnace and AC unit. Presidential roof completed in 2022, trex decking on upper decks, outside kitchen, waterfall, natural gas fire pit and hot tub. The outside entertainment areas are sure to please the fussiest. The house is close to the walking trail and shopping, it is a perfect Lynden location.

Picture yourself coming home to a space thats been thoughtfully updated, where new carpet and lighting create a warm, inviting atmosphere. After a day of classes at Western or a productive day at work, youll park in your dedicated, covered spot, knowing your bike is stored securely in the covered racks nearby. Catch up with friends in the open and bright living space, this condo is all about making life simple and comfortable. Everything you need is within easy reachgrab a workout at the on-site gym, or relax in the green spaces around the complex. With easy access to downtown Bellingham, Fairhaven, and trails for those weekend adventures, this home offers both convenience and a sense of calm. Start building your future!

Opportunity awaits in this rare corner lot Duplex located in a quiet community near Fairhaven. The highly desirable 3 bedroom and 1.5 bath floorplan in each unit makes it perfect for multi generational living, an investor looking to maximize rental income, or a savvy buyer looking to subsidize their mortgage payment. Property has been updated with a new roof, all brand new windows, new carpeting, and fresh exterior/interior paint. Comes with driveway space for 4 vehicles (2 for each unit) and is fully stocked with all appliances, including a washer/dryer in each unit. Both units were rented this year for $1, 800/month (below market average due to long term tenants), but both units are vacant and ready for you!

Welcome to 1318 E McLeod Road in the sought-after Northern Heights neighborhood. This charming tri-level home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 1, 864 sqft of comfortable living space on a generous lot. The main level features a practical layout with two bedrooms, a welcoming living area, kitchen, and dining space that opens to the deckideal for outdoor gatherings. Downstairs, youll find two additional bedrooms, a bonus space perfect for a rec room or office, and access to the outdoor area. The spacious backyard provides ample room for your hobbies and outdoor activities. Centrally located, this well-loved home is ready for its next chapter. Make it yours today!

Imagine coming home after a refreshing morning run or paddle at Lake Padden just steps from your front door, or a short ride to Galbraiths world-class mountain biking trails! This inviting 3 bedroom, 2.25 bath home is your gateway to an active lifestyle. Fresh updates like a new roof, interior paint, stylish fixtures and remodeled guest bathrooms offer comfortable PNW living. The expansive .33-acre lot features mature landscaping and gardening space in a newly fenced backyard, perfect for relaxation or hosting gatherings. With Whole Foods, REI and other amenities minutes away, everything you need is within reach. Embrace a life where nature meets convenience and community in this sought-after neighborhoodhomes here don't come up often!

First time on the market! Parklike 4.9-acre property features a 5-bedroom, 2.25-bath tri-level home and a 30x96 shop. Meticulously taken care of with tasteful updates make this property a true gem! The home boasts a formal living and dining area on the main level, a kitchen and breakfast nook that opens to the deck, a laundry room and a half bath. The upper level includes a primary bedroom and a 3/4 bath, plus two additional bedrooms and a full bath. The lower level offers a daylight basement with a family room and two finished rooms, along with an unfinished 780 sq ft basement. Lg 2 car garage. Wired for a generator. Sandy loam soil. Room for horses. Located in the Lynden School District, just 10 min from Lynden and 7 min to I-5.

Fabulous opportunity. This custom built home sits on over 1/2 acre with over 100 feet of waterfront in the prestigious Boundary Ridge neighborhood in Semiahmoo. Views from the San Juan Islands to Point Roberts, Tsawwassen and more. Access the beach from the adjacent beach path. Enjoy all the amenities that Semiahmoo offers from the award winning golf course, marina and Resort Semiahmoo.The home is in need of some TLC and repair. It is reflected in the price. The opportunity is tremendous! the spacious layout is fantastic for entertaining and quiet living. The main floor features the primary bed, living room, kitchen and dining with access to enormous deck overlooking the bay and beyond.

Looking for single level living? Check out this 1-story custom home built by Rosendahl-Hancoop on .91 acre parcel w/ 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and bath. Large primary with on-suite includes separate shower, soaking tub and walk-in closet and private entry off the back deck. Huge picture windows throughout the home brings in abundant natural light. The kitchen offers breakfast bar and eating nook. Spacious living room and dining area or combine the two rooms to create a great room! The 840sq/ft detached shop offers 2-bays w/ nat'l gas heat, 220 power and setup for generator. Expansive covered back deck with a hot tub ready pad plumbed w/ 220 pwr. Convert the shop into an ADU or keep it and build an ADU or two. Buyer to verify with COB.

text: Stunning Beach Access Home in Blaine, WA!Discover coastal living at its finest with this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, ideally located in the serene and scenic city of Blaine, WA. Enjoy the coastal breeze, stunning views, and easy beach access, perfect for morning walks or sunset strolls.Experience the best of Pacific Northwest living in this prime locationyour dream home awaits!

Rare opportunity in the sought after Samish neighborhood...literally steps from Lake Padden Park! Nestled on 1.77 acres, you'll discover this delightful 4 bedroom 3, 000+ sq ft home plus detached shop! Radiating PNW charm, the vibe here is part mid century modern & part Craftsman, resulting in a warm & inviting home with generously sized rooms. The private primary suite encompasses the entire upper floor & features a fireplace, sitting area, multiple walk in closets (with a second washer & dryer) and luxurious ensuite bathroom. This is an oasis in the city...walk or bike to Galbraith, the park & lake within minutes or relax & entertain on the spacious deck. Detached shop is loaded with potential with bathroom plumbing already in place.

This Lynden School District gem is a standout property on 4.7 fenced acres. Updated w/a fresh exterior look, including 7-new windows, brand-new roof, & new paint for both the house & the shop. The home features a spacious, open floor plan w/a cozy fireplace & real hardwood floors, in main entry, living room, & kitchen. Enjoy 3-beds+ versatile den/office could serve as 4th bed. w/ space for 5th bed. There are 2.5 bathrooms, & large bonus room above attached two-car garage provides additional living space. Primary bed. conveniently located on main floor. 24x36 shop is a notable feature, equipped w/a 1-bed., 3/4 bath apt. & approx. 700 sq. ft. of space. Shop also includes dbl. overhead doors, wired for generator (gen. remains), & RV parking.

Welcome to this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, perfectly situated on a spacious, flat lot surrounded by serene woods. With fresh interior and exterior paint, new flooring and trim, and brand-new appliances, this home is move-in ready! You'll love the ample covered parking, providing plenty of space for your vehicles and recreational toys. Ideal as a starter home or for those looking to downsize, this gem offers the perfect balance of comfort and outdoor space. Located in a highly desirable area of the County, you'll enjoy easy access to Blaine, Lynden, and Ferndale, while still maintaining a peaceful, private setting. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity. This home is a must see!

Escape the ordinary and step into this one-of-a-kind octagonal home, where breathtaking ocean and mountain views meet modern design. Drenched in natural light from high ceilings and abundant skylights, this unique property offers indoor and outdoor living experience unlike any other. This home features 2 beds + den/office & 2 baths, modern kitchen with stainless appliances, wrap around deck, metal roof, full basement/garage and a private backyard. Dont let this architectural delight pass you by!

Welcome to the Robin Lane Community, where this well-maintained, move-in ready home awaits! Bathed in natural light, the open layout flows seamlessly, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The spacious primary bedroom features a luxurious en suite bathroom, while the large laundry room and ample storage throughout the home add to its functional charm. Step out to the covered patio, perfect for relaxing or entertaining, with plenty of space for gardening, plus a shed for your tools and extra storage. The carport and ample parking are added bonuses. With easy access to parks, trails, the bus line, and the vibrant Fairhaven shops and businesses, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience!

Welcome home to this stunning property in Nooksack! Step inside & get ready to be amazed. The living room features stained shelves & beams with black brackets, adding a modern & stylish touch. The fireplace features marble/stone, douglas fir beams, a TV bracket & stand. The kitchen has soft-close dove-tail cabinets, black quartzite sink, quartz countertops, & a black matte appliance package with slide-in oven. Ginormous 12x25 covered porch in the back is perfect for entertaining. The landscaping is a beautiful & low-maintenance. Upgraded front door & garage door adds a touch of elegance to the home. The exposed concrete in the driveway & porches adds durability & style. Come experience the beauty & craftsmanship firsthand.

Welcome to Birch Bay! This fixer-upper is a great opportunity to create your dream home just a short walk from the beach. Nestled on a greenbelt lot, the spacious yard has potential for landscaping improvements and revitalizing the existing pond and flower gardens. Inside, the 4-bedroom layout boasts vaulted ceilings but needs some updates to reach its full potential. The large master suite features a jetted tub, perfect for a remodel. With new flooring and painted white trim already in place, you can easily add your personal touch. This property is a blank canvas waiting for your vision. Dont miss this chance to invest in a home in a beautiful location and make it uniquely yours!
